{
  "keyword": "ADDCMNE",
  "description": "Add Communications Entry (ADDCMNE)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "SBSD",
      "description": "Subsystem description",
      "help": "Subsystem description (SBSD)\n\nSpecifies the name and library of the subsystem description to which the communications entry is being added or in which it is being changed.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Subsystem description\n\nNote: The IBM-supplied object QSYSSBSD is not valid on this parameter.\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "SBSD",
          "description": "Subsystem description",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": true,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "positional": 1
    },
    {
      "name": "DEV",
      "description": "Device",
      "help": "Device (DEV)\n\nSpecifies the name of the device description or the type of the device being used with this communications entry.\n\nNote: You must specify a value on either this parameter or the Remote location (RMTLOCNAME) parameter, but not both.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *ALL, *APPC, *ASYNC, *BSCEL, *FINANCE, *INTRA, *RETAIL, *SNUF",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 10
      },
      "positional": 2,
      "valueMap": {
        "*FINANCE": "*FIN",
        "*RETAIL": "*RET"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "RMTLOCNAME",
      "description": "Remote location",
      "help": "Remote location (RMTLOCNAME)\n\nSpecifies the name of the remote location used with this communications entry. The remote location name specified in the associated device description can be used here. No validity checking is done on the remote location name.\n\nNote: You must specify a value for either this parameter or the Device (DEV) parameter, but not for both.",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 8
      },
      "positional": 3
    },
    {
      "name": "JOBD",
      "description": "Job description",
      "help": "Job description (JOBD)\n\nSpecifies the name and library of the job description used for jobs that are started as a result of receiving a program start request, and that are processed through this communications entry. If the job description does not exist when the entry is added or changed, a library qualifier must be specified because the qualified job description name is kept in the subsystem description.\n\nNote: Only a user with all object (*ALLOBJ) special authority is allowed to add or change an entry for which the job description does not exist.\n\nSingle values\n\nQualifier 1: Job description\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": false,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "singleValues": [
        "*USRPRF",
        "*SBSD"
      ],
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "JOBD_LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "JOBD",
          "description": "Job description",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "defaultValue": "*USRPRF"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 4
    },
    {
      "name": "DFTUSR",
      "description": "Default user profile",
      "help": "Default user profile (DFTUSR)\n\nSpecifies the default user profile used for a program start request that contains no security information. This user profile is not used for program start requests that contain a password or specify a user profile (either valid or not valid).\n\nNote: The names QDFTOWN, QLPINSTALL, QSECOFR, QSPL, QDOC, QDBSHR, QRJE, QTSTRQS, and QSYS are not valid entries for this parameter.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *NONE, *SYS",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*NONE",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "MODE",
      "description": "Mode",
      "help": "Mode (MODE)\n\nSpecifies the mode name of the communications device or remote location name whose communications entry is being added or changed.\n\nNote: The names SNASVCMG and CPSVCMG are not valid for this parameter.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *ANY",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*ANY",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "MAXACT",
      "description": "Maximum active jobs",
      "help": "Maximum active jobs (MAXACT)\n\nSpecifies the maximum number of jobs (received program start requests) that can be active at the same time through this communications entry.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *NOMAX",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*NOMAX",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "minValue": 0,
        "maxValue": 32000,
        "numericOnly": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "code": "ADDCMNE SBSD(ALIB/SBS1) DEV(COMDEV)"
    }
  ],
  "source": {
    "url": "https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/ssw_ibm_i_74/cl/addcmne.htm",
    "version": "IBM i 7.4"
  },
